sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1335001
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: Vh p53 + Ig hinge + his tag + HlyA
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Naturally, nanobodies are present in camelids family, however we decided to use the approach of bacterial production. The gene was synthesized by GenScript company.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Vh p53 is responsible for the production of nanobodies that have an affinity to p53 protein: this interaction can be used in cancer detection.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes:  The gene is not in standard pSB1C3 plasmid but in pUC57 vector, but it contains standard prefix and suffix.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Luiza Niyazmetova
